{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"copy"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray","text":"NSArray<MLNPolygon *>"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"polygons"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon\/polygons"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon"]]},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"polygons","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMultiPolygon(py)polygons","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","title":"polygons","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"polygons"}]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon\/polygons"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An array of polygons forming the multipolygon."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon","title":"MLNMultiPolygon","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPolygon"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polygons that do not overlap. For example, you could use a multipolygon shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to represent the body of land that consists of an island surrounded by an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll: the inner island would be one "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon"},{"type":"text","text":" object, while the surrounding"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"group of disconnected but related buildings."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolygon":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolygon","title":"MLNPolygon","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPolygon"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a closed shape consisting of four or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"vertices, specified as "},{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the edges that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use a polygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"building, a lake, or an area you want to highlight."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon/polygons":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon\/polygons","title":"polygons","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon\/polygons","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"polygons"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An array of polygons forming the multipolygon."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}]}}}